      <div class="card-sub">Event timeline shows how bias evolves over a story's lifecycle. Parallel coordinate plots compare 4+ outlets more clearly than radar.</div>
      <div class="card-detail">
        <div style="font-size:11px;color:var(--text2);line-height:1.8">
          <strong style="color:#fff">→</strong> Event timeline: bias score evolution per story across time + outlet entry points<br>
